No interpretations. Just…

816
00:44:04.516 --> 00:44:07.287
It's just Harmony
and dissonance.

817
00:44:07.311 --> 00:44:09.247
Harmony. dissonance.

818
00:44:09.271 --> 00:44:11.666
No. I know. I just
needed to talk it all out.

819
